    <item>
      <title>摩根大通指数发布日期临近，印度储备创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-s-reserves-hit-record-as-jpmorgan-index-date-draws-near</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于外国投资者在印度债券被纳入摩根大通旗舰新兴市场债务指数前纷纷买入印度债券，印度的外汇储备上周增至 6515 亿美元的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-s-reserves-hit-record-as-jpmorgan-index-date-draws-near</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 06:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员警告不要急于进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员对进一步降息的前景做出了谨慎的评估，寻求更多通胀进展的证据，以确保任何宽松政策都是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 05:44:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行维持利率不变，等待新莫迪政府上台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-central-bank-keeps-rates-steady-as-modi-coalition-awaited</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正如预期的那样，印度央行维持基准利率不变，在意外选举结果导致政策不确定性的情况下继续关注通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-central-bank-keeps-rates-steady-as-modi-coalition-awaited</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 04:34:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 供应计划震动市场，油价料将周度下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+ 意外计划今年恢复部分供应，导致油价周度下跌，促使该联盟的一些成员国向市场保证他们致力于保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 23:29:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
